data.description: Welcome to this charming single-level home with a delightful mid-century vibe and a spacious garage/shop on a .75 acre lot! This meticulously maintained property offers a seamless blend of retro charm & modern convenience. The open layout creates an inviting atmosphere, perfect for both relaxing & entertaining. The well-appointed garage & shop provides ample space for hobbies or storage, & there is also RV parking! The large parking area is also a bonus! Maybe consider this property if you are a mechanic, landscaper or have a small business needing space. Conveniently located close to local amenities, easy access to I-84, equipped with space for RVs or toys this home offers the perfect blend of comfort & convenience with no HOA. Roof is approx 7years old, shop is partially heated with 220 power. With its desirable features and prime location, plus do not miss out on the rare Incense cedar trees in the front yard, this home is a true gem!
